setDetails.setDescription:
Eldar Venture is our early-stage token fund, seeking to invest in recent crypto projects that have a promising use case and huge market potential, in order to provide VC-like returns.

Eldar Venture selects early crypto projects that have an exceptional founding team, an innovative working product and significative early growth. Most of the tokens selected are also backed by a set of prominent crypto VC firms.

You can learn more about our investment process at: https://www.eldarcap.com/investment-process
setDetails.managerDescription: Eldar Capital is a premier crypto asset manager which creates and maintains top-level crypto funds accessible by everyone.
